    "Before unblinding, most instructors correctly guessed which answers were GPT-generated.",
    "Instructors noted several trends differentiating GPT-4 answers from student answers:",
    "• GPT-4 answers to questions that required the interpretation of experimental data were long, excessively wordy, and often included accurate but un-requested information and/or explained simple ideas that were obvious but not required for the answer, e.g.",
